ANNEXURE
.
.
The reasons of re-opening and approval are attached with this notice and your retuen have been
replicated and accepted againest notice u/s148.
In furthence of pending proceedings u/s 147, it is requested to furnsih the following information for F.Y-
2015-16 relevent to AY- 2016-17:-
(i) Please furnish the copy of balance sheet, P&L account with all annexures and notes, independent
auditor report, tax audit report and computation of income.
(ii) Please furnish a detailed note on the business activity carried out during the year consideration.
(iii) Please furnish the detail of share premium recieved during the year alongwith its valuation report
u/s 11UA.
(iv) The valuation report with respect to the working of EPS and justification for the quantum of
premium.
(v) The comparison of the working of EPS and share premium with the immediately prior instance,
wherein the shares were allotted with premium.
(vi) Please furnish the details of expenses incurred on account of increased in capital during the year.
(viii) Please furnsih the complete details of goodwill created and deperation claimed on it during the
year consideration.
(viii) Please furnish the detail of accounting and taxation treatment of the goodwill, depreation on it and
share premium received during the year consideration.
